      • getGroupSpace

        public float getGroupSpace()
        Returns the space that is left out between groups of bars. Always returns 0 if the BarData object only contains one DataSet (because for one DataSet, there is no group-space needed).
        Returns:

      • setGroupSpace

        public void setGroupSpace(float percent)
        Sets the space between groups of bars of different datasets in percent of the total width of one bar. 100 = space is exactly one bar width, default: 80
        Parameters:
        percent -
